      "value": "dependencies:\n  markast: ^0.1.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Luego ejecuta:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "flutter pub get"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Desde 0.1.0 el paquete incluye un "
        },
        {
          "type": "bold",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "parser Markdown → AST nativo en Dart"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " además del renderer. No necesitas Python en producción si el contenido se parsea en la app."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Verificar la instalación"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "dart",
      "value": "import 'package:markast/markast.dart';\n\nvoid main() {\n  final doc = parse('# Hola, **markast**!');\n  print(doc.toJson(indent: 2));\n}"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Ruta local (desarrollo)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Si estás trabajando con una copia local de la librería:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "yaml",
      "value": "dependencies:\n  markast:\n    path: ../flutter_markast"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Parser Python (opcional)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Si prefieres pre-procesar Markdown en un build server o CMS, instala el parser Python:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "pip install markast"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Produce exactamente el mismo formato JSON que "
        },
        {
          "type": "code_inline",
          "value": "parse()"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " en Dart, así que el renderer Flutter es idéntico para ambos orígenes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "python",
      "value": "from markast import parse\n\ndoc = parse(\"# Hola, **markast**!\")\nprint(doc.to_json())"
    },
